    <briefdescription>
<para>Component that stores information about the last damage received. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Used to track which entity last dealt damage to this entity. This enables attribution of kills for scoring and other game logic. The damage context is updated by the damage system when damage is applied. </para>
